WEBVTT

25:32.200 --> 25:32.800 line:80%
I do.

25:33.720 --> 25:35.320 line:80%
I dream about it every night.

25:36.000 --> 25:38.020 line:80%
Then what if everything
the authorities said

25:38.020 --> 25:39.680 line:80%
when they closed the case was a lie—

25:39.680 --> 25:40.680 line:80%
what would you do?
